net.ligreto.data
Class Column

java.lang.Object
  net.ligreto.data.Column
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
public class Column
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>

This class is used to copy the column values from the database result set and store them for later usage. It is mainly used for finding duplicate entries with the same join columns and aggregated result calculation.

Author:
Julius Stroffek
